  "title": "Links to repo of the v1 examples are broken",
  "body": "**Do you want to request a *feature* or report a *bug*?**\r\nBug\r\n\r\n**Bug: What is the current behavior?**\r\nWhen going to https://community.algolia.com/instantsearch.js/v1/examples/, the links to the repo of each example are erroring with a 404:\r\n- https://github.com/algolia/instantsearch.js/tree/master/docs/examples/media\r\n- https://github.com/algolia/instantsearch.js/tree/master/docs/examples/e-commerce\r\n- https://github.com/algolia/instantsearch.js/tree/master/docs/examples/tourism\r\n\r\n**Bug: What is the expected behavior?**\r\nThey should link to the GitHub directory holding the code (could not find it, sorry)",
